name: KiboShib
description: KiboShib (KIBSHI) is the first AI-generated meme coin. On December 8th 2022, AI was tasked with creating a meme coin. It all started as a joke, but the idea which was proposed by the AI is so powerful that nobody could resist! The AI even suggested a logo design which later has been fed to the AI image generator. The age of AI is upon us, and KiboShib stands for exploring the capabilities of AI with a hopeful outlook.
